* How to?

* How to? - Step 1. Preparing

0. Install git
1. Get sources

  $ git clone https://go.googlesource.com/go
  $ cd go

2. Configure Git to use Gerrit
3. Sign the CLA

or use *go-contrib-init*

  $ go get -u golang.org/x/tools/cmd/go-contrib-init
  $ cd /code/to/edit
  $ go-contrib-init

.link https://golang.org/doc/contribute.html https://golang.org/doc/contribute.html

